data.description: SELLERS SAY SELL!!!Welcome home to this spacious bay area home! The elegant doorway leads you into 2 large areas that can be used for living or dining.  Featuring tray ceilings, tile floors throughout, plenty of natural light, and a custom built-in. You'll love all this home has to offer.  The kitchen boasts an oversized bar top great for entertaining, new appliances and plenty of cabinet space. Also includes a separate bedroom suite-perfect for guests. You'll love admiring your spacious yard from your beautiful extended covered patio.  Hurry and show this one- it won't last long!
